                        <td>
                        
                            <h1><strong>Sustaining economic growth in a changing climate</strong></h1>

<p>On 19 and 20 July, the IGC will be hosting international and Bangladeshi researchers, policymakers, industry leaders, and development practitioners for the &#39;<a href="https://www.theigc.org/events/resilient-and-resurgent-bangladesh" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Resilient and resurgent Bangladesh: Sustaining economic growth in a changing climate</a>&#39; conference. The engaging two-day programme will take place in Dhaka, with sessions livestreamed to online audiences.</p>

                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody></table>
				
                
				
