<p>IGC and Yale&#39;s Economic Growth Center will be co-hosting the <a href="https://www.theigc.org/events/igcegc-conference-firms-trade-and-development" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">&#39;Firms, trade, and development conference&#39;</a> on 19 and 20 October, 2023. The <a href="https://lse.tfaforms.net/f/IGC-EGC-CallforPapers" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">call for papers</a> is now open until 14 August.<br/>
